e Inn all the way back on this platform. Give him the bag. You'll get about 3/4 of a blue per turn-in at level 20, and a plat or 2. Now just gate back to SK and do it again. It's insanely boring, and you have to make sure you keep your skills up (except alteration..it'll be going up with the gating) but the exp is really nice if you want to avoid stupid pickup groups in LoIO. Just make sure you keep up on your skills!<br>
<br>
Fizzlebuster<br>
