1-4 Newbie Steamfont<br>
4-8 GFay Orc Hill<br>
8-12 Orc's in EC<br>
12-18 Two spawn Siren in OOT, aqua goblins, etc..<br>
18-20 Arena Aviak Spawn with a little help in Lake Rathe<br>
20-24 Highkeep Hold, the inside, guard room.<br>
24-26 Grouped in Loio<br>
26-30 Quadding the 4spawn goblin tower in Loio<br>
30-34 Grouped in OT If you are good, very easy to get a group.<br>
34-44 Soloing in OT. I grabbed clarity, and soloed across the hill near the FM ledge.<br>
44-46 Happ in LFay Load up shield, skin and Conflag, stun, ice shock. Very easy, don't go AFK, the horse will kill you. Harmtouched me for 400 like 9 times.<br>
This is where I retired him, maybe I will come back someday. For now, he is sitting nekked in the EC tunnel. Thank you for your help in getting him that high. GL with your own Wizards.<br>
