<br>
1-8: Solo in Nek forest...newbie log area<br>
8-11: Solo/Grouped in Lavastorm<br>
11-12: Solo in East Commonlands (spiders, snakes, etc.)<br>
12-20: Solo in Oasis kiting crocs<br>
20-29: Grouped at Treants in South Karana<br>
29-31: Solo at Dwarves in OOT. Three spawns, tremendous exp<br>
31-35: Solo at gnolls in South Karana (solo kiting)<br>
-&gt; Acquired Journeyman's Boots at level 35<br>
35-41: Solo at Gnome guards in Steamfront<br>
41-46: Solo/Grouped at Spectres in Feerrott<br>
46-50: Solo/Duo at Freeport Guards in East Freeport and Ogre Guards outside Oggok<br>
51-54: Spirocs in Timorous Deep and Raptors (pre-nerf when they were all indifferent, solo kite)<br>
55-57: Grouped in Sebilis/Chardok/Howling Stones<br>
57-60: Solo in Neriak doing Ogres/Trolls, Brownies in Lesser Faydark<br>
<br>
During certain parts I also did some dungeon groups...Najena in my early teens on occasion, Cazic-Thule a bit in my 30s and Lower Guk and Solusek B in my 40s. Did some exp in Sebilis, Chardok, and Howling Stones in my 50s as well.<br>
