<br>
38-44 Big mixture here folks... I switched between grouping and soloing in Great Divide, partnering with chanter in Eastern Wastes, and grouping in Dreadlands... I soloed exclusively in EW (giants, walruses, anything I could find, single-kite giants for faction/exp/loot or quad kite walruses)<br>
<br>
45 and 46 Happ Dremblenod folks, I died once on this camp and thats cuz Pained Unicorn messed me up, level 45 = 19 hours total, no loot tho<br>
