47-50 Solo kiting spirocs in Timorous Deep and grouping in Karnor's Castle<br>
<br>
51-52 Kiting Spirocs like mad<br>
<br>
53-54 Mixture of Velks groupage, Seb groupage, and soloing Cyndreela, she's great for loot and xp folks, easiest solo for 51+<br>
<br>
I'm finishing up 54 on seb and Cyndreela now... at 55 I'm planning to do Raptors... 57+ I'm hoping to just group, and 59-60 I'm looking forward to brownie guards, Lfay...<br>
<br>
Good luck folks! /rant on Don't get down cuz of the constant dissing of the class, whatever happens, we'll always be useful.  I for one love my class, but sometimes get pissed when I don't get groups.  Next day I go to seb, get crypt group, and see a cleric be LFG for an hour or two... And no matter what peeps tell you, you can ALWAYS solo, I mean, look at necromancers, they have it worse off than we do.  /rant off<br>
